{"tid":131821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自我感覺良好","createTime":"2017-02-23T10:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T10:58:27.000Z","uid":9259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6177053f7340c90262cae08b178cc740cdf1ab2","tid":131821,"uid":9259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人真係好佩服嗰d點都覺得自己好叻既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠有人點做得差做得差都有籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個同學<br />\n跑步輸:好唔慣新鞋個底囉<br />\n打波輸:唉啱啱感冒完真係幾唔舒服<br />\n考試炒:今次都冇讀 讀左點只呀<br />\n我次次聽到就心諗<br />\n有邊次得呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"5014513400e967ddb20557a7bb20d782b8f41cc5","tid":131821,"uid":79137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"自我感覺欠佳點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14faaab696d17cfd2776e20e629a4b403c276247","tid":131821,"uid":9259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自我感覺欠佳點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欠佳都有欠佳問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1ca41885505df8f2ced66a4b4a477dbc8dccf5","tid":131821,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"一笑置之就好"},{"pid":"890bf197b629b533be2f80f38b90ad07ebd5b851","tid":131821,"uid":9259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一笑置之就好</blockquote><br />\n我正常都係<br />\n但佢又成撚日要出風頭<br />\n柒左又比籍口真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no